text: The 2011 Supertaça de Angola (24th edition) was contested by Recreativo do Libolo, the 2010 Girabola champion and Petro de Luanda, the 2010 Angola cup winner. On home court, ASA beat Interclube 1–0 to secure their 1st title as the away match in ended in a scoreless draw. ==Match details== ===First Leg=== {| width=92% |- | | |} {| width="100%" |valign="top"
